data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home with a new roof, updated PVC plumbing & electric. LVP flooring throughout. Very spacious open-floor plan perfect for holiday gatherings. There's a large open living room & dining room, remodeled open kitchen with bar, a huge separate Florida room -perfect as an extra family room, game room or large office. Split bedrooms. (One of the 3 guest rooms is currently being used as a large laundry & utility & storage room.) Super cozy covered back porch off the Florida room overlooking a large fenced in backyard. Detached oversized 1 car garage with workshop that has plumbing & 50 amp electrical (for an RV.) Long oversized driveway. Beautiful circular street with very little traffic.
